  "detailed_description": "This is an extremely cozy, laid-back strategy Puzzle Game.<br><br>It is a low-stakes, 'move at your own pace' kind of game.<br><br>Stack the blocks, make a solid line, watch the rocks crumble and fall!<br><br>I made this in about 2 days, and was inspired by a Mobile Game Ad I saw.<br>The ad was fake and pre-rendered, but it looked so fun that I decided to make it in real life, for people to enjoy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/25228411d462b14048d0cdeb6dd45a20.poster.avif?t=1739739028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/25228411d462b14048d0cdeb6dd45a20.webm?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/25228411d462b14048d0cdeb6dd45a20.mp4?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can play this game for <strong>hours</strong> and still have fun strategizing which blocks you should place where, to break the next line.<br><br>I spent so much time playing this, when I should have been developing a trailer for it.<br>The sound effects are extremely satisfying, and the visuals are pleasing to the eyes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/490cac31b460a0d336133df3b5be7b39.poster.avif?t=1739739028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/490cac31b460a0d336133df3b5be7b39.webm?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/490cac31b460a0d336133df3b5be7b39.mp4?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It is <strong>infinitely replayable</strong>.<br><br>Hope you enjoy this simple little game I made!",
  "about_the_game": "This is an extremely cozy, laid-back strategy Puzzle Game.<br><br>It is a low-stakes, 'move at your own pace' kind of game.<br><br>Stack the blocks, make a solid line, watch the rocks crumble and fall!<br><br>I made this in about 2 days, and was inspired by a Mobile Game Ad I saw.<br>The ad was fake and pre-rendered, but it looked so fun that I decided to make it in real life, for people to enjoy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/25228411d462b14048d0cdeb6dd45a20.poster.avif?t=1739739028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/25228411d462b14048d0cdeb6dd45a20.webm?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/25228411d462b14048d0cdeb6dd45a20.mp4?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can play this game for <strong>hours</strong> and still have fun strategizing which blocks you should place where, to break the next line.<br><br>I spent so much time playing this, when I should have been developing a trailer for it.<br>The sound effects are extremely satisfying, and the visuals are pleasing to the eyes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/490cac31b460a0d336133df3b5be7b39.poster.avif?t=1739739028\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/490cac31b460a0d336133df3b5be7b39.webm?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2810410/extras/490cac31b460a0d336133df3b5be7b39.mp4?t=1739739028\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>It is <strong>infinitely replayable</strong>.<br><br>Hope you enjoy this simple little game I made!",
